# House Price Prediction

## 📌 Overview
This project predicts house prices using Machine Learning.

## 🛠️ Technologies
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib

## ⚙️ Features
- Data preprocessing
- Model training using Linear Regression
- Price prediction
- Data visualization

## 📊 Results
- Model predicts house prices based on area and bedrooms
- Shows positive correlation between area and price

## 📈 Conclusion
- Area is a key factor affecting house price
- The model performs well on given data
